Detailed Description

cvmx_gmx::_rx_bp_drop#

GMX_RX_BP_DROP = FIFO mark for packet drop

Notes: The actual watermark is dynamic with respect to the GMX_RX_PRTS register. The GMX_RX_PRTS controls the depth of the port's FIFO so as ports are added or removed, the drop point may change.

In XAUI mode prt0 is used for checking.
